content: Absolutely terrible. It's required for my physics class which sucks because you have to pay for it and it's finicky, hardly gives you any direction when answering questions, and straight up doesn't work sometimes.
NL12 is completely broken. I'm required to do that lesson for a course but I cant because the start button doesnt work. Overall a terribly buggy and outdated app.
Not an effective way of learning
